criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Hepatocellular carcinoma is confirmed by tissue pathology or in accordance with
             clinical diagnosis standard;

          -  ECOG score 0-1;

          -  HCC BCLC grading 0, A, B, C;

          -  Child-Pugh score prior to therapy A and B;

          -  As judged by investigators, the patient can comply with the study protocol;

          -  Patient voluntarily participates in this study, understands the process of the study,
             and is willing to sign the written consent form.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  HCC BCLC grading D;

          -  Child-Pugh score prior to therapy C.
